Pointa ta UTF-8 strang ta be converted up in place.
.BE

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Da first three routines convert tha case of individual Unicode characters:
.PP
If \fIch\fR represents a lower-case character,
\fBTcl_UniCharToUpper\fR returns tha correspondin upper-case
character n' shit.  If no upper-case characta is defined, it returns the
characta unchanged.
.PP
If \fIch\fR represents a upper-case character,
\fBTcl_UniCharToLower\fR returns tha correspondin lower-case
character n' shit.  If no lower-case characta is defined, it returns the
characta unchanged.
.PP
If \fIch\fR represents a lower-case character,
\fBTcl_UniCharToTitle\fR returns tha correspondin title-case
character n' shit.  If no title-case characta is defined, it returns the
correspondin upper-case character n' shit.  If no upper-case characta is
defined, it returns tha characta unchanged. Y'all KNOW dat shit, muthafucka!  Title-case is defined
for a lil' small-ass number of charactas dat gotz a gangbangin' finger-lickin' different appearizzle when
they is all up in tha beginnin of a cold-ass lil capitalized word.
.PP
Da next three routines convert tha case of UTF-8 strings up in place in
memory:
.PP
\fBTcl_UtfToUpper\fR chizzlez every last muthafuckin UTF-8 characta up in \fIstr\fR to
upper-case.  Because changin tha case of a cold-ass lil characta may chizzle its
size, tha byte offset of each characta up in tha resultin strang may
differ from its original gangsta location. I aint talkin' bout chicken n' gravy biatch.  \fBTcl_UtfToUpper\fR writes a null
byte all up in tha end of tha converted string.  \fBTcl_UtfToUpper\fR returns
the freshly smoked up length of tha strang up in bytes.  This freshly smoked up length is guaranteed
to be no longer than tha original gangsta strang length.
.PP
\fBTcl_UtfToLower\fR is tha same ol' dirty as \fBTcl_UtfToUpper\fR except it
turns each characta up in tha strang tha fuck into its lower-case equivalent.
.PP
\fBTcl_UtfToTitle\fR is tha same ol' dirty as \fBTcl_UtfToUpper\fR except it
turns tha straight-up original gangsta characta up in tha strang tha fuck into its title-case equivalent
and all followin charactas tha fuck into they lower-case equivalents.

.SH BUGS
.PP
At dis time, tha case conversions is only defined fo' tha ISO8859-1
characters.  Unicode charactas above 0x00ff is not modified by these
routines.

